TYPE_HIDDEN

public static final byte TYPE_HIDDEN
User is available, but another users see this status as not available. This status is sent only by clients, server translate it to TYPE_NOT_AVAILABLE.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

TYPE_HIDDEN_DESCR

public static final byte TYPE_HIDDEN_DESCR
User is available, but another users see this status as not available with description. This status is sent only by clients, server translate it to TYPE_NOT_AVAILABLE_DESCR.
